WEBVTT

00:00.528 --> 00:01.815
<i>Before there was sex,</i>

00:01.935 --> 00:04.632
<i>before there was the city,</i>
<i>there was just me,</i>

00:04.752 --> 00:08.154
<i>Carrie... Carrie Bradshaw</i>
<i>from Castlebury, Connecticut.</i>

00:08.156 --> 00:09.522
(Voice breaks)
My parents kicked me out.

00:09.524 --> 00:10.756
I was hoping
he could stay with us.

00:10.758 --> 00:11.824
Of course he can stay.

00:11.826 --> 00:13.893
Seeing my parents' faces
made me feel bad

00:13.895 --> 00:15.027
about what I'm doing.

00:15.029 --> 00:16.896
You being gay... that is
their issue, not yours.

00:16.898 --> 00:18.864
These are
your college applications.

00:18.866 --> 00:20.533
Time to start planning
your future.

00:20.535 --> 00:22.705
Never, ever become friends with
one of my boyfriends again.

00:22.825 --> 00:23.484
Okay.

00:23.604 --> 00:24.819
Cool party. I'm Scott.

00:24.939 --> 00:26.705
You don't have to talk to me
if it bugs you.

00:26.707 --> 00:28.307
No! I-I like it.

00:28.309 --> 00:29.942
My dad... he's gonna give me
an allowance

00:29.944 --> 00:31.010
to find a place in Manhattan.

00:31.012 --> 00:32.411
What do you think
about the flat?

00:32.412 --> 00:34.613
I think I can make this work.

00:34.615 --> 00:36.215
Ooh, you are gonna
adore it here!

00:36.217 --> 00:38.450
(Carrie) - You gonna be good here?
- Yeah.

00:38.570 --> 00:40.691
